            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "They left beating of Paul, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " lest they should have been set upon by the soldiers, for breaking the peace, &c. The fear of man caused them to forbear what the fear of God could not. ",
        "children": []
